Package io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.modeling

This package includes classes and interfaces that support creation of solver-specific modeling objects, such as variables, constraints, etc. for multiple solvers and algebraic modeling languages.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MsdxSolverModelingFactory
    This interface provides the template for creating and using all solver-specific modeling objects, Variables, Constraints, Objectives, and Terms.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MsdxCplexModelingFactory
    This class implements the methods used to create solver-specific modeling objects for IBM's CPLEX solver.
    You need to have a licensed copy of IBM CPLEX in order to use this code.
    MsdxLpTextModelingFactory
    This class implements the methods used to create modeling objects to write an .lp text file representation of an optimization model.
    MsdxLpTextModelingFactory.Constraint
    This class is part of the API for the .lp "solver"
    MsdxLpTextModelingFactory.Expression
    This class is part of the API for the .lp "solver"
    MsdxLpTextModelingFactory.Objective
    This class is part of the API for the .lp "solver"
    MsdxLpTextModelingFactory.Term
    This class is part of the API for the .lp "solver"
    MsdxLpTextModelingFactory.Variable
    This class is part of the API for the .lp "solver".
    MsdxModel
    This class provides a basic implementation of an optimization problem using a solver.
    MsdxMpsTextModelingFactory
    This class implements the methods used to create modeling objects to write an .mps text file representation of an optimization model.
    MsdxMpsTextModelingFactory.Constraint
    This class is part of the API for the .mps "solver"
    MsdxMpsTextModelingFactory.Expression
    This class is part of the API for the .mps "solver"
    MsdxMpsTextModelingFactory.Objective
    This class is part of the API for the .mps "solver"
    MsdxMpsTextModelingFactory.Term
    This class is part of the API for the .mps "solver"
    MsdxMpsTextModelingFactory.Variable
    This class is part of the API for the .mps "solver"
    MsdxSolverModelingObject
    This class represents the common elements across all solver-specific modeling objects.
